      • createDrawing2

        public static String createDrawing2(Carport carport)
        This method creates a long String by appending lines of SVG code to a StringBuilder. The SVG lines are generated from small seperate methods that depend on a Carports measurements. The returned String translates into a drawing of a carport with roof.
